# ============================================================
# SISBEN del paciente
# ============================================================

### Registrar SISBEN del paciente
POST {{base}}/api/patients/5/sisben
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sisbenGroupId": 105,
  "score": 35.50,
  "sisbenCard": "SISB-2024-00123",
  "surveyDate": "2023-06-15",
  "validFrom": "2024-01-01",
  "validUntil": null,
  "current": true,
  "observations": "Encuesta vigente 2024"
}

###

### Listar SISBEN del paciente
GET {{base}}/api/patients/5/sisben
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Obtener SISBEN por ID
GET {{base}}/api/patients/5/sisben/5
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Eliminar SISBEN
DELETE {{base}}/api/patients/1/sisben/1
Authorization: {{token}}

###

# ============================================================
# Seguridad social del paciente
# ============================================================

### Registrar afiliación de seguridad social
POST {{base}}/api/patients/5/social-security
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payerId": 3,
  "regimenId": 15,
  "affiliationCategoryId": 13,
  "affiliationTypeId": 10,
  "affiliationNumber": "AF-2024-00456",
  "cotizanteThirdPartyId": null,
  "isBeneficiary": false,
  "affiliationDate": "2024-01-01",
  "validFrom": "2024-01-01",
  "validUntil": null,
  "current": true,
  "observations": "Cotizante activo EPS"
}

###

### Listar seguridad social del paciente
GET {{base}}/api/patients/5/social-security
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Obtener afiliación por ID
GET {{base}}/api/patients/5/social-security/5
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Eliminar afiliación
DELETE {{base}}/api/patients/5/social-security/5
Authorization: {{token}}

###

# ============================================================
# Contratos del paciente
# ============================================================

### Asociar contrato al paciente
POST {{base}}/api/patients/5/contracts
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contractId": 2,
  "policyNumber": "POL-2024-00789",
  "validFrom": "2024-01-01",
  "validUntil": "2024-12-31",
  "current": true,
  "observations": "Póliza EPS Sura vigente"
}

###

### Listar contratos del paciente
GET {{base}}/api/patients/5/contracts
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Obtener contrato del paciente por ID
GET {{base}}/api/patients/5/contracts/5
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Desasociar contrato del paciente
DELETE {{base}}/api/patients/1/contracts/1
Authorization: {{token}}

###

# ============================================================
# Verificación de cobertura (HU-019A)
# ============================================================

### Verificar derechos (sin servicio específico)
GET {{base}}/api/patients/5/coverage-verification
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Verificar cobertura de un servicio específico
GET {{base}}/api/patients/5/coverage-verification?serviceId=3
Authorization: {{token}}
